Class ListTools

java.lang.Object
com.taco.tacository.util.tools.list_tools.L
public final class ListTools extends Object

A static utility class containing functions used to easily add ListTools.OperationResponder ListChangeListeners to an ObservableList.

      @Contract("_, _, _, _ -> new") @NotNull public static <E> @NotNull OperationHandler<E> wrap​(@Nullable @Nullable ReentrantLock lock, @Nullable @Nullable String name, @NotNull @NotNull javafx.collections.ObservableList<E> list, OperationListener<E> listener)

      Wraps the specified OperationListener instance in an OperationHandler object.


      Details

      1. Keep in mind, OperationHandler is itself an implementation of OperationListener.
      2. The constructed OperationHandler instance passes its OperationListener method definitions to the specified OperationListener parameter.

      Examples


      OperationListener Passthrough

      @Override
 public void onPermutate(Operation<E> op, Operation<E> op2) {
     listener.onPermutate(op, op2);
 }
